Message.message: Many years have passed since the events of Heroes of Sokoban II.
Dragons have vanished from the realm, never to be seen again.
And new heroes have cropped up, as if there were only room for so many beings in one world.
No one can resist the bard's music.
Orange druid turns stone into wood, wood into stone.
Living things may also be turned into stone.
Try not to think about the moral implications, and don't do it any more than necessary.
